title: Blackalicious - Imani Vol 1 (2015) 320kbps
description:
From Wikipedia:
"In 2015, after ten years since releasing a project together, Gift of Gab and Chief Xcel announced the fourth Blackalicious album Imani Vol. 1. The group partnered up with PledgeMusic to give dedicated fans the opportunity to purchase the album and other special items, with over 120% of the project's goal funds being met.[19] Imani Vol. 1 was released on September 18, 2015, and was well-received by critics."

This is an AMAZING album that's been well worth the wait!

PLEASE, PLEASE, PLEASE support the artist by purchasing the album, merch, and ESPECIALLY going to see them live if you can.

Peace, love, and respect.

ENJOY!
